/>\n石蔭石梨上堆城門行山去堆園都仲得[/quote]<br />\n無錯！不過要幾個人行，始終入夜一兩個行都好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d266bdcb8dbe984b0bff0b1988bad9d99947c022","tid":1504571,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"不反對通知書到幾多點？"},{"pid":"cab332763e69f03a6cd10f617f8eb2c60b5c9842","tid":1504571,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"葵褔路向葵芳方向<br />\n左邊任何一個路口可去葵興<br />\n或大窩口"},{"pid":"76847728974d2cadcad94847a65da74aa91f0859","tid":1504571,"uid":107147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d266bdcb8dbe984b0bff0b1988bad9d99947c022","tid":1504571,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"不反對通知書到幾多點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"From HK01<br />\n遊行申請人林啟康指，在聆訊中與警方就路線達成共識，並已經獲得825遊行的不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n活動於明日下午2時30分在葵涌運動場集合，下午3時起行， 經興盛路、葵福路、德士古道行人天橋、楊屋道、馬頭壩道、永順街，終點為荃灣公園中央廣場。遊行將於下午7時結束，參加者可於荃灣公園集會至下午8時。"},{"pid":"b848e516f290aa3f093ee9f921d01ce71db2ae0a","tid":1504571,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"嘉里Kerry logistics<br />\n入去有條樓梯上葵盛<br />\n好隱蔽的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHM2Drp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHM2Drp.jpg&h=d7443a76&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個位入去"},{"pid":"8f722e5e553d548dd13e696055f6601653498dd8","tid":1504571,"uid":107147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab332763e69f03a6cd10f617f8eb2c60b5c9842","tid":1504571,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"葵褔路向葵芳方向<br />\n左邊任何一個路口可去葵興<br />\n或大窩口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"葵興大窩口好近狗署，一有咩事塞路落石蔭散"},{"pid":"d09a2d1aba95d3b98c7d314985ef28fea5958556","tid":1504571,"uid":107147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b848e516f290aa3f093ee9f921d01ce71db2